37:54.520 --> 37:57.160
but six months to a year, it's very, very quick.

37:58.120 --> 38:01.720
So you're looking at velocities in the oil and gas world

38:01.720 --> 38:05.960
that are literally 10 times faster than the velocities in the minerals world.

38:06.840 --> 38:13.720
