39:58.440 --> 40:03.000
which still takes you on the same path of foreign minds, foreign refining,

40:04.200 --> 40:08.840
questionable labor practices, all of which in principle can be fixed and made transparent.

40:08.840 --> 40:12.360
In principle, it's just, it's not there right now.

40:12.360 --> 40:13.080
It's not where we are.

