44:21.560 --> 44:24.840
If that were true, if they were inherently simpler,

44:24.840 --> 44:26.120
that might be true.

44:26.120 --> 44:27.640
It would be inherently cheaper to make.

44:27.640 --> 44:28.840
But it's not true.

44:28.840 --> 44:31.400
The battery is not like the little double-A cell

44:31.400 --> 44:33.320
you stick in a child's toy.

44:33.320 --> 44:38.440
This half-ton engine, it's actually an electrochemical engine,

44:39.000 --> 44:40.600
has thousands of parts in it.

44:41.480 --> 44:44.360
If it's a Tesla battery, maybe tens of thousands of parts,

44:44.360 --> 44:48.520
but lots of batteries, thousands of parts, tens of thousands of welds,

44:48.520 --> 44:52.440
cooling systems, electronic control systems, structural systems.

44:52.440 --> 44:57.000
It's a complicated, multi-thousand-part electrochemical engine.

44:57.640 --> 44:58.520
The motor is simple.

44:58.520 --> 45:00.040
Electric motor has two moving parts.

45:00.760 --> 45:04.280
In an internal combustion engine, we just flop the complexities.

45:04.840 --> 45:07.240
The fuel tank has two moving parts.

45:07.240 --> 45:10.920
It's an electric motor that pumps your fuel, two moving parts.

45:10.920 --> 45:11.720
A little tiny one.

45:12.520 --> 45:13.400
The tank has nothing yet.

45:13.400 --> 45:14.840
It's just fluid.

45:15.400 --> 45:17.320
The engine, on the other hand,

45:17.320 --> 45:20.280
instead of being an electrochemical engine with thousands of parts,

45:20.280 --> 45:23.320
it's a thermochemical engine with thousands of parts.

45:24.280 --> 45:27.960
We've just swapped mechanical, thermo-mechanical complexity

45:27.960 --> 45:30.040
for electrochemical complexities.

45:30.040 --> 45:31.320
They're both complex.

45:31.880 --> 45:35.880
They both wear out at the molecular level.

45:35.880 --> 45:38.360
Wear and tear on an engine with reciprocating parts

45:38.360 --> 45:39.880
is literally at the molecular level.

45:41.320 --> 45:46.440
Batteries wear out, electrochemistry wears out at the molecular level.

45:46.440 --> 45:50.680
They both have performance characteristics that vary with temperature,

45:51.400 --> 45:53.400
all kinds of both have safety issues.

45:54.920 --> 45:59.400
The difference between them is that the complicated fuel tank

46:00.520 --> 46:05.880
in an electric car is made of expensive minerals

